Bootstrap-Grid: 

    container/container-fluid-->Root element 
    row-->parent flex container
    col-->flex items size

    col-{breakpoint}-{no of columns}
        breakpoint-->xs,sm,md,lg,xl
        columns-->1-12
    
    order:
        order-{breakpoint}-{order sequence}

    justify-content:
        justify-content-{breakpoint}-{value}
        value-->center,start,end,around,between

    offset:
        offset-{breakpoint}-{0-12}

    align items:
        align-items-{breakpoint}-{start,end,center,stretch}

    align self:
        align-self-{breakpoint}-{start,end,center,stretch}


Bootstrap colors:
    colors:
        primary
        secondary
        danger
        warning
        success
        info
        light
        dark
        white
        muted
        body        
        white-50        
        black-50

Bootstrap Text
    text-{colors}
    text-{breakpoint}-{align value} -->  align value-->justify,left,right,center
    text-truncate
    text-break
    text-{uppercase,lowercase,capitalize}

    font-weight-{bold,bolder,normal,light,lighter}
    font-italic

    text-monospace

    text-reset

    text-decoration-none
   


Bootstrap background colors
    bg-{color,transparent}

Bootstrap Border
    border --->All four sides
    border-{top,bottom,left,right} --->Selective sides
    border-0 --->No border
    border-{top,bottom,left,right}-0 --->No border at given side
    border-{color} --->For border color

    Border Radius
        rounded
        rounded-{sides}
        rounded-circle
        rounded-pill
        rounded-0

Bootstrap Display Property
    d-{breakpoint}-{values}

    values-->inline,block,inline-block,flex,inline-flex,none

    eg. d-md-block

Bootstrap Spacing
    margin:
        m-{breakpoint}-{value}
        m{sides}-{breakpoint}-{value}

        sides-->t,b,l,r,x,y
        value-->0-5,auto
        eg. ml-auto

    margin:
        p-{breakpoint}-{value}
        p{sides}-{breakpoint}-{value}

        sides-->t,b,l,r,x,y
        value-->0-5
        eg. pl-5

Bootstrap Visibility
    invisible
    visible

Bootstrap Shadow
    shadow
    shadow-{none,sm,lg}

Bootstrap Overflow
    overflow-{auto,none}